WEBVTT

00:10.010 --> 00:11.563
- I need to know why.

00:18.639 --> 00:22.125
- There are so many things
no one has the answers for.

00:27.786 --> 00:28.925
- What does that mean?

00:30.720 --> 00:32.860
- Why we lose the
people we love.

00:34.379 --> 00:35.931
Death.

00:35.932 --> 00:37.071
Pain.

00:38.003 --> 00:39.003
Change.

00:40.350 --> 00:43.353
Sadly, it's all a part of life.

00:50.015 --> 00:51.153
You're trying to figure out

00:51.154 --> 00:54.157
if there's something you
could've done to stop this.

00:59.266 --> 01:01.129
We'll never know
why people elect

01:01.130 --> 01:03.063
to take away the
blessing of life.

01:03.960 --> 01:05.789
There's nothing you
could have done.

01:08.171 --> 01:09.931
We all have our time.

01:11.381 --> 01:15.075
Unfortunately, she decided to
make that decision on her own.

01:23.152 --> 01:24.152
- She left me.

01:29.813 --> 01:34.232
- Try to remember
her as she was:

01:35.647 --> 01:37.097
a loving mother,

01:38.891 --> 01:40.169
a human being.

01:44.587 --> 01:46.968
I will pray for her
soul, young man.

